{"tid":187262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[桃花依舊] 查比高恩斯終極決戰國民體育會","createTime":"2017-04-04T21:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T10:21:02.000Z","uid":40940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62528b46900a1271cb0602086e4cdf364aae82dc","tid":187262,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:02:35.000Z","msg":"查比高恩斯去年11月飛往哥倫比亞，準備參加南美球會盃決賽時遇上空難。事後南美足協直接將球會盃冠軍獎盃，頒給查比高恩斯以示悼念。<br />\n<br />\n所以查比高恩斯將以南美球會盃冠軍的身份，與南美自由盃盟主哥倫比亞國民體育會，爭奪「南美超級盃」。<br />\n<br />\n國民體育會專機抵埗時獲射水致敬，職球員落機時獲夾道歡迎，他們之後坐當局安排的消防車前往酒店，民眾沿途鼓掌致意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/9/509/17498105509/17496709331_600x327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F9%2F509%2F17498105509%2F17496709331_600x327.jpg&h=2cda010d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年尾遇上空難的巴甲球隊查比高恩斯，上月再度登上國際航班，是在發生慘劇後的首次。<br />\n<br />\n從Instagram社交網站的合照所見，查比高恩斯一行30人都面帶笑容，看來沒有受到導致71人罹難的撞山意外影響。報道指出，空難中3名生還球員的2人希里奧尼圖（Helio Nrto）與阿倫路斯舒爾（Alan Ruschel）均有隨大軍出發，為大部分新隊友打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比賽link 6:15am開波<br />\n<a href=\"http://livetv.sx/enx/eventinfo/518190_chapecoense_atletico_nacional/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivetv.sx%2Fenx%2Feventinfo%2F518190_chapecoense_atletico_nacional%2F&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f5a3052a\" target=\"_blank\">http://livetv.sx/enx/eventinfo/518190_chapecoense_atletico_nacional/</a>"},{"pid":"6172a95062d39416e53c9336f17e847b52bd9f3d","tid":187262,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:07:54.000Z","msg":"查比高恩斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f25c6048a5ddd920a288b525b5443b90354c9de","tid":187262,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:50:29.000Z","msg":"反cup 2:1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4510e32a166016318743430e0581100ae79fbaa4","tid":1